[ a                      owl:Axiom ;
  rdfs:comment           "This  demonstrates  that  the  immune  serum\nspecifically recognizes the MUT-7 protein and that MUT-7 is\nexpressed  in adult worms, and localizes to both  the nucleus and the cytosol." ;
